    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/5c6ae9a34906566cbb629c726ce76cc2.avif?t=1753347264\" width=600 height=280 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💫做出选择，引发混乱！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nobi-Nar13 星系曾是宇宙中最无聊的地方……直到 Carmen 驾驶她的太空卡车到来，吸引了一群最健谈、最调皮的生物。你能驾驭这场混乱吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/3a80e09f6e8353e2c2bc3668f767fa1d.poster.avif?t=1753347264\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/3a80e09f6e8353e2c2bc3668f767fa1d.webm?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/3a80e09f6e8353e2c2bc3668f767fa1d.mp4?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌟解开时髦谜题！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《SPACE DIVA》是一段疯狂、离经叛道、毫不掩饰、混乱又可爱的故事——专为离婚人士、话痨，以及追求纯粹、无过滤乐趣的人打造。骄傲呈现，毫无高雅可言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/f4151a05d637daf04dd28766553910ac.poster.avif?t=1753347264\" width=600 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/f4151a05d637daf04dd28766553910ac.webm?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/f4151a05d637daf04dd28766553910ac.mp4?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👩‍🚀爆笑分支对话</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演 Carmen —— 一位有些迷糊的中年流浪者，驾驶着她的太空卡车在无尽宇宙中漫游。她的车辆装满了这些年来搜集的失物招领品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/f9b2c5984267ad5157decf19d6e04887.poster.avif?t=1753347264\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/f9b2c5984267ad5157decf19d6e04887.webm?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/f9b2c5984267ad5157decf19d6e04887.mp4?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🫦投递闪亮物品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >途中，她遇到了一些好奇又古怪的角色，他们寻求她的帮助。但要小心——她的“解决方案”可能会帮他们解决问题……也可能让事情变得更糟！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/ad170f27ca3ee7565e313e4269d442cb.poster.avif?t=1753347264\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/ad170f27ca3ee7565e313e4269d442cb.webm?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044510/extras/ad170f27ca3ee7565e313e4269d442cb.mp4?t=1753347264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👽准备好迎接疯狂了吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫画剧情 —— 故事以漫画小段呈现，充满华丽幽默。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜爽感 —— 简单易上手，轻松又令人满足的谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2000年代氛围 —— 充满 2000 年代的流行文化梗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分支剧情 —— 多个结局与决定组合，体验丰富变化。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于工作室：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rave Team 是一家来自西班牙的新兴工作室，专注于打造非传统、疯狂又疯癫的叙事体验。我们将流行文化的魅力与都市文化的叛逆融合，致力于为游戏行业带来前所未有的创新故事。</p>",
